OL,5,Cmeasures
OL,7,FThe watchdog said data from the prison
OL,8,Fshowed 130 inmates ` 20% of those
OL,9,Feligible for release ` had been held
OL,10,Fillegally after their release date in
OL,11,Fthe last six months.
OL,13,FThe backlog in sentencing calculations
OL,14,Falso meant 10 prisoners had been
OL,15,Freleased early "in error" between July
OL,16,F2024 and June 2025.
