OL,7,FIn a letter to the Justice Secretary,
OL,8,Fthe chief inspector said arrangements
OL,9,Ffor new prisoners' first night at the
OL,10,Fnorth London jail and induction were
OL,11,F"chaotic and even frightening".
OL,13,FMen were held in dirty cells missing
OL,14,Fbedding, furniture, telephones and
OL,15,Fpillows, the watchdog said, while the
OL,16,Fmajority of prisoners were locked in
OL,17,Ftheir cells for more than 22 hours a
OL,18,Fday.
