OL,7,FThe report also said 60% of prisoners
OL,8,Fwere sharing cells that were designed
OL,9,Ffor one person, many living areas were
OL,10,Fdirty and there was a widespread
OL,11,Finfestation of mice and cockroaches.
OL,13,FInspectors took emergency action after
OL,14,Fthey found care of vulnerable
OL,15,Fprisoners under constant supervision
OL,16,Fwas "shockingly poor", with one prison
OL,17,Fofficer found asleep, two were reading
OL,18,Fbooks and another was "completely
OL,19,Fabsent".
