OL,7,FThe "unacceptable practices" in
OL,8,Flooking after these prisoners, deemed
OL,9,Fat serious risk of self-harm, were a
OL,10,Fparticular concern for inspectors
OL,11,Fgiven three suicides at the jail in
OL,12,F2025.
OL,14,FMr Taylor said: "Pentonville is an
OL,15,Fovercrowded, inner-city, Victorian
OL,16,Fprison with a record of poor
OL,17,Fperformance over many years.
OL,26,@oD@EOUoD@\O]vD@QOU
