OL,5,Cmeasures
OL,7,F"Too many of its staff have become
OL,8,Fdisillusioned about the possibility of
OL,9,Fimprovement or their capacity to
OL,10,Faffect change. Yet many of its
OL,11,Fshocking failures are firmly within
OL,12,Fthe control of leaders.
OL,14,F"The governor will need significant
OL,15,Fsupport and investment from HM Prison
OL,16,Fand Probation Service to strengthen
OL,17,Fhis senior leadership team, re-focus
OL,18,Fon the basics, and put in place
OL,19,Feffective oversight and assurance
OL,20,Fsystems to turn this failing prison
OL,21,Faround."
