OL,7,FA survey of prisoners also revealed
OL,8,F44% told inspectors they felt unsafe
OL,9,Fat the time of inspection, which the
OL,10,Fwatchdog said was the highest figure
OL,11,Frecorded during his tenure as chief
OL,12,Finspector.
OL,14,FPentonville is the 10th prison to be
OL,15,Fissued with an urgent notification
OL,16,Fsince November 2022, following Exeter,
OL,17,FCookham Wood Young Offender
OL,18,FInstitution, Woodhill, Bedford,
OL,19,FWandsworth, Rochester, Manchester and
OL,20,FWinchester prisons.
