OL,4,Cafter release date put in special
OL,5,Cmeasures
OL,7,FThe emergency measure was introduced
OL,8,Fin 2017 as a way to raise immediate
OL,9,Fconcerns following an inspection,
OL,10,Fwhich requires a response and action
OL,11,Fplan by the Justice Secretary within
OL,12,F28 days.
OL,14,FElsewhere, the inspector's report also
OL,15,Ffound when releases were planned, 23%
OL,16,Fof those prisoners were homeless on
OL,17,Fthe day they were released, and very
OL,18,Ffew had employment on release.
