OL,7,FAndrew Neilson, director of campaigns
OL,8,Fat the Howard League for Penal Reform,
OL,9,Fsaid the findings of the inspection
OL,10,Fwere "outrageous" and represent a "new
OL,11,Flow" for an overcrowded public service
OL,12,Fon the brink of collapse.
OL,14,FHe added: "While the Government
OL,15,Finherited a dire state of affairs in
OL,16,Fprisons, it has had more than a year
OL,17,Fto bring about change.
