OL,7,F"As report cards go, such a dire
OL,8,Faccount of dysfunction in Pentonville
OL,9,Finstils little confidence that
OL,10,Fministers have a grip of the
OL,11,Fsituation."
OL,13,FPrisons minister Lord James Timpson
OL,14,Fsaid he visited the prison on
OL,15,FThursday, where the team is already
OL,16,Fworking to urgently address the
OL,17,Fconcerns raised by the chief inspector.
OL,19,FAn action plan will also be published
OL,20,Fin the coming weeks to support the
OL,21,Fefforts.
